Module iu.util.type
Package edu.iu.type

Interface IuAnnotatedElement

All Known Subinterfaces:
IuAttribute<D,T>, IuConstructor<C>, IuDeclaredElement<D>, IuExecutable<D,R>, IuField<D,T>, IuMethod<D,R>, IuNamedElement<D>, IuParameter<T>, IuProperty<D,T>, IuType<D,T>
public interface IuAnnotatedElement
Facade interface for annotated type elements.

This interface supports backwards compatibility for annotations on elements defined using legacy annotation types. For example, if a type is marked with javax.annotation.Resource, it will automatically be translated to jakarta.annotation.Resource.
